snippet.title: Bomb Bee - Arcade - By Pac-Man Creator Toru Iwatani (Namco 1979)
snippet.description:
Bomb Bee arcade, a video pinball game by Pac-Man creator Toru Iwatani, released the year before the release of a little yellow circle he created named Pac-Man.

Flip over to the history of Pac-Man, at The Dot Eaters:
http://thedoteaters.com/?bitstory=pac-man

http://www.thedoteaters.com  Video Game History 101

-~-~~-~~~-~~-~-
View the goofy glitch that makes playing Access Software's classic game Leader Board Golf so much fun: 
https://youtu.be/HnEN942x5rY
-~-~~-~~~-~~-~-
